  <brief_title>Evaluation of Pelvic Peritonization in Low Anterior Resection for Rectal Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Pelvic Peritonization in Low Anterior Resection for Rectal Cancer: A Multicentric Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
